{
  "type": "guide",
  "title": "Accept Payments Overview",
  "meta": {
    "description": "",
    "hidden": false
  },
  "blocks": [
    {
      "id": "12af5248-6fe8-4792-af80-cba147106e03",
      "type": "callout",
      "props": {
        "variant": "nutshell"
      },
      "content": "Accept mobile money and card payments from customers across Africa. Choose between a Vesicash-hosted checkout page or a direct integration built into your own UI.",
      "meta": {}
    },
    {
      "id": "20b5d6c0-a8c1-43d8-a552-ba9fc0cbbde2",
      "type": "callout",
      "props": {
        "variant": "before-you-begin"
      },
      "content": "- You have completed KYC and generated API keys.\n- You have set your `secret_key` and `public_key` in your environment.\n- You have configured a `webhook_url` to receive event notifications.",
      "meta": {}
    },
    {
      "id": "72cbf902-bc18-44ed-a44b-ce03238e94fe",
      "type": "prose",
      "props": {
        "variant": "heading",
        "level": "h2"
      },
      "content": "Hosted Checkout Flow",
      "meta": {}
    },
    {
      "id": "d368de02-658d-4544-bb3f-8205ceb554c4",
      "type": "prose",
      "props": {
        "variant": "body"
      },
      "content": "The simplest integration. Vesicash collects payment details on a hosted page — no card data touches your server.",
      "meta": {}
    },
    {
      "id": "a1b2c3d4-0001-4000-8000-000000000001",
      "type": "steps",
      "props": {},
      "content": null,
      "meta": {},
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "58737a8b-8673-4645-b8a0-6bbeca597a71",
          "type": "step",
          "props": {
            "number": 1,
            "title": "Initialize the payment",
            "description": "Call `POST /api/v1/transactions/initiate`. Vesicash returns a `payment_link` and a `reference`.",
            "last": false
          },
          "content": null,
          "meta": {}
        },
        {
          "id": "0997b0ce-017a-4e1b-a9ef-c7f256dc5821",
          "type": "step",
          "props": {
            "number": 2,
            "title": "Redirect the customer",
            "description": "Send the customer to `data.payment_link`. Vesicash handles card data collection and 3DS2 entirely.",
            "last": false
          },
          "content": null,
          "meta": {}
        },
        {
          "id": "812910f6-39af-4320-b251-e304e31ac5dd",
          "type": "step",
          "props": {
            "number": 3,
            "title": "Handle the redirect",
            "description": "After payment, Vesicash redirects to your `redirect_success_url` or `redirect_failed_url` with `?payment_reference=<ref>` appended.",
            "last": false
          },
          "content": null,
          "meta": {}
        },
        {
          "id": "51043438-b6b6-4303-bcd6-94389689d13e",
          "type": "step",
          "props": {
            "number": 4,
            "title": "Verify the outcome",
            "description": "**Always** confirm with `GET /api/v1/transactions/{{reference}}/status` before fulfilling the order. Never rely on redirect parameters alone.",
            "last": true
          },
          "content": null,
          "meta": {}
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "86bf0595-c1ae-4acd-a892-c1e96ee1f9a8",
      "type": "prose",
      "props": {
        "variant": "heading",
        "level": "h2"
      },
      "content": "Direct Integration Flow",
      "meta": {}
    },
    {
      "id": "3b9c492c-7d5e-43a4-89eb-3909da8d5994",
      "type": "prose",
      "props": {
        "variant": "body"
      },
      "content": "Build your own payment UI. You collect card details and submit them directly to Vesicash.",
      "meta": {}
    },
    {
      "id": "b8c2e5a1-4f6d-4b8e-9c3a-7d5f1e2b4c8a",
      "type": "steps",
      "props": {},
      "content": null,
      "meta": {},
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "d117eec1-5c92-490b-b5d2-65ea023c6e74",
          "type": "step",
          "props": {
            "number": 1,
            "title": "Initialize the payment",
            "description": "Call `POST /api/v1/transactions/initiate` with `integration_type: \"DIRECT_API\"`. You receive a `reference` — no `payment_link` is returned.",
            "last": false
          },
          "content": null,
          "meta": {}
        },
        {
          "id": "24afa8f9-2702-4709-a9d9-c7870a2371f8",
          "type": "step",
          "props": {
            "number": 2,
            "title": "Collect and submit card details",
            "description": "POST the customer's card details and device fingerprint to `POST /api/v1/transactions/{{reference}}/pay`.",
            "last": false
          },
          "content": null,
          "meta": {}
        },
        {
          "id": "49f7e1be-c65c-4fb3-9c9a-a478dc63c90b",
          "type": "step",
          "props": {
            "number": 3,
            "title": "Handle 3DS2 challenge (if required)",
            "description": "If the issuer returns `challenge_required`, display the ACS challenge to the customer and await the webhook confirmation.",
            "last": false
          },
          "content": null,
          "meta": {}
        },
        {
          "id": "4f5eec39-a643-4ab7-a789-10add988c289",
          "type": "step",
          "props": {
            "number": 4,
            "title": "Verify the outcome",
            "description": "Call `GET /api/v1/transactions/{{reference}}/status` to confirm `status: \"success\"` before fulfilling the order.",
            "last": true
          },
          "content": null,
          "meta": {}
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "334091ab-5812-4d5d-b47c-9f81ec3f01a7",
